{"tid":910103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［狂賀］突破限制 解放軍將校夢想成真 乘搭運輸機在航母蒸氣彈射","createTime":"2018-11-21T02:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T02:03:32.000Z","uid":101051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"71ec7eb5fd398d1d286c846056545da2d5c741ea","tid":910103,"uid":101051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:03:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181120/58936614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F58936614&d=ALGqpQX7p98fRTqHuUgWuDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=88643676\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F58936614&h=007c5dd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181120/58936614</a><br />\n<br />\n美國核動力航空母艦列根號剛完成與菲律賓軍方的聯合軍事演習，目前身處南中國海國際水域。《蘋果》記者昨日特別獲邀請登艦參觀，深入艦橋、船艙等重地，並走上甲板直擊超級大黃蜂戰機升降實況。列根號司令官表示，連場軍演僅屬恆常訓練，旨在加強與當地海軍合作，但無正面回應是否為向中國施壓。記者發現，<span style=\"color: red;\">駐港部隊司令員譚本宏亦有獲邀上船。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲要隻航母出到公海<br />\n又係用核動力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}